1
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,039
As a tower,

2
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,140
the studio is too conspicuous

3
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,820
and easily discovered by others.

4
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,440
So,

5
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,240
this place

6
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,600
is the real tower.

7
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,480
Because of Allen,

8
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:21,400
this case couldn't be closed as an accident.

9
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:25,570
You haven't had time to clean up these places.

10
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,880
On the bedsheets,

11
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:34,960
we can definitely find your and Mu Weijie's DNA.

12
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,840
If you still deny it,

13
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:39,600
we can run trace evidence analysis.

14
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,600
You really are a cop.

15
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,000
Very impressive.

16
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,880
Makes sense.

17
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,680
Whatever happens,

18
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,880
always leaves a trace.

19
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,960
The day Rongrong got hurt,

20
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,360
I actually knew

21
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,620
she had gone through the same thing as me.

22
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,320
That night,

23
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,920
she suddenly asked me to keep her company at her place.

24
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,240
And her expression,

25
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,720
her demeanor,

26
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,760
I was all too familiar with them.

27
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:21,000
Because I had already

28
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,760
experienced all of this myself.

29
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,440
I will never forget that day.

30
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,320
It was raining.

31
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,120
I was soaked.

32
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,760
He offered to drive me.

33
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:38,800
In the end.

34
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,480
I fell asleep.

35
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,360
We're here.

36
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,260
Mr. Mu, this doesn't seem to be where my house is.

37
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,480
Did we go the wrong way?

38
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,720
Mr. Mu, if there's nothing else, I'll be going.

39
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,120
Thank you, sir.

40
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,640
Come back.

41
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,080
Xiaoyue.

42
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:52,120
Mr. Mu, you can't do this.

43
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,040
Mr. Mu.

44
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,120
Don't hide.

45
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:02,200
Help! Help!

46
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,600
Help!

47
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,920
Be good, Xiaoyue.

48
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,000
Help!

49
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,800
Help!

50
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,760
Help!

51
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,440
You can't escape.

52
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,120
Xiaoyue.

53
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,000
Be more obedient next time.

54
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,640
Look.

55
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,720
So violent.

56
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,600
You even broke this.

57
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,900
This doesn't seem to be the direction to your house.

58
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,240
Xiaoyue.

59
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,370
I advise you not to call the police.

60
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:44,140
I guarantee your reputation will be ruined.

61
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,880
You'd better think about your mother.

62
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,080
Think about your mom.

63
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,040
Since that day,

64
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,720
every day has been a nightmare.

65
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,360
And I have to pretend nothing's wrong at home.

66
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,700
I'm afraid my mom will notice something's wrong

67
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,840
and worry about me.

68
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,420
What about your boyfriend, Alan?

69
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,720
Wasn't he with you?

70
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,690
Of course I wanted him to be with me.

71
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,340
But when I was in the most pain,

72
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,000
he couldn't give me any comfort.

73
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,280
Excuse me.

74
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,500
I need to take this.

75
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,090
Hello, Qiaoyue.

76
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,800
What are you doing?

77
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,720
Just tell me what you want.

78
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,780
I'm busy right now.

79
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,690
Where are you right now?

80
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,680
Where else could I be?

81
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,880
A friend just introduced me to a client.

82
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,480
We're discussing business.

83
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,480
I miss you.

84
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,440
Okay, okay.

85
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,520
I'll go see you when I'm done, alright?

86
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,380
I can't just leave my client here.

87
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:10,040
But I want to see you right now.

88
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,920
I've had enough of this.

89
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,180
You do this every time.

90
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,320
I'm working.

91
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,650
I'm not fooling around.

92
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,520
We're discussing a big project.

93
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,360
If it goes well, we'll have money to buy a house.

94
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,200
Okay?

95
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,880
Can you just trust me a little?

96
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,360
Who is it?

97
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,400
Hello, ma'am.

98
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:52,800
Who are you?

99
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:53,960
I am

100
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:56,080
an instructor at Qiaoyue Art Studio.

101
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,080
My last name is Mu.

102
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,480
Mr. Mu,

103
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,940
I've heard a lot about you.

104
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,880
Come, come.

105
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,940
Please have a seat.

106
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,130
I bought some fruit for you.

107
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:08,250
I'll put it on the coffee table.

108
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,600
Xiaoyue,

109
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,680
look who's here.

110
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:13,960
Ma'am, it's fine.

111
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,080
I'll go find her.

112
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:16,800
Okay.

113
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,360
Xiaoyue, come out.

114
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,480
Mr. Mu has been here for a while.

115
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,960
You should come greet him.

116
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,000
Ma'am, she's out.

117
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,680
Mom, sit.

118
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,520
Let Mr. Mu sit down.

119
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,360
Qiaoyue,

120
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,520
I came today

121
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,720
just to see how you're doing.

122
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,560
You haven't seemed yourself in class lately.

123
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,160
I'm doing very well.

124
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:50,400
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

125
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,360
Oh, really?

126
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,280
Let Mr. Mu sit down.

127
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,160
Let him sit down.

128
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,640
Ma'am, I'll seat myself.

129
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,000
Xiaoyue,

130
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:07,360
pour Mr. Mu a glass of water.

131
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,640
What's wrong?

132
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,570
My hand slipped.

133
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:18,920
Feed me.

134
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,520
What happened?

135
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,600
My hand slipped.

136
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,760
Ma'am, I'm sorry.

137
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:30,080
I spilled some water on the floor myself.

138
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,740
Please don't mind her, Mr. Mu.

139
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,800
This child grew up without a father.

140
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,200
And I'm blind.

141
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,770
I didn't raise her well.

142
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,580
Ma'am, please don't say that.

143
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,640
I think you raised her very well.

144
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,160
She's a wonderful child.

145
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,120
Is she?

146
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:43,720
She

147
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,400
has a real talent for painting.

148
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,570
I came here this time

149
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:50,640
mainly to tell you something.

150
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:56,320
I specially selected some of Xiaoyue's best works

151
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,920
to exhibit at an art exhibition.

152
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:01,320
I... I am blind.

153
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,240
I can't see.

154
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,000
It's fine, ma'am.
